{"tid":2449605,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[左膠大愛] 非法入境者人數急升　美國土安全部長：情況受控","createTime":"2021-03-16T22:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T23:42:52.000Z","uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"601dbf08d79db9d0e10fe8e790ccf21ec507d0f2","tid":2449605,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T22:01:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580967-20210317.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580967-20210317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixYpVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=a8e60337\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580967-20210317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3e9af157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580967-20210317.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"26091e34e95f4952cfbda8d2ca4b3ee05784eaa9","tid":2449605,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T23:25:29.000Z","msg":"湧入美國的非法入境者人數激增，國土安全部長馬約卡斯強調，情況受控，又為容許單獨入境兒童留下的政策辯護。<br />\n<br />\n總統拜登上任後修改非法移民政策，允許18歲以下單獨越過美墨邊境進入美國的非法移民留低，等候當局決定，他們是否獲准合法居留，至於非法入境的家庭及成年人就會被遞解出境。<br />\n<br />\n馬約卡斯承認，非法入境兒童人數急升，在新型冠狀病毒疫情下，對邊境巡邏和其他部門構成挑戰，形容邊境情況「困難」。<br />\n<br />\n馬約卡斯說，主要來自中美洲的非法入境未成年人，八成在美國都有親屬，其中四成的父或母在美國。<br />\n<br />\n2月有9400多名兒童單獨越境進入美國，較1月激增六成 。共和黨把非法入境者大量湧入，歸咎是拜登的政策導致。民主黨內部的進步派人士抨擊拜登政府，把非法入境兒童扣留在邊境拘留中心超過72小時。"},{"pid":"34ccb48ceaa2d0e05a1158c2c7e1caac780b7e88","tid":2449605,"uid":287269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T23:27:12.000Z","msg":"激增六成都受控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好包容"},{"pid":"639097dcb5540b04fa5826616571044c3f06aa49","tid":2449605,"uid":48276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T23:29:30.000Z","msg":"唔準開槍唔比打佢地<br />\n兒童偷渡係咪無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1510b69bb35476cc9677fa7bf6b00586feb1615a","tid":2449605,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"639097dcb5540b04fa5826616571044c3f06aa49","tid":2449605,"uid":48276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T23:29:30.000Z","msg":"唔準開槍唔比打佢地<br />\n兒童偷渡係咪無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T23:42:52.000Z","msg":"打死左拜登玩咩?"}]}